<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1437,151,863]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,414,694,719]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Taxonomic notes.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Alexander. All" authorityYear="1953" box="[430,741,694,719]" class="Insecta" family="Ptychopteridae" genus="Bittacomorphella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thaiensis">
<emphasis box="[430,741,694,719]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Bittacomorphella thaiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is readily separated from other 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Alexander, Alexander" authorityYear="1965" box="[1147,1343,694,719]" class="Insecta" family="Ptychopteridae" genus="Bittacomorphella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1147,1343,694,719]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Bittacomorphella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the combination of a wing membrane lacking macrotrichia and one white band on the leg. Alexander’s 1953 description notes that the 
<typeStatus box="[443,539,768,792]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">paratype</typeStatus>
has a locality of, “Near Wat at Doi Sutep, Chengmai, 
<date box="[1161,1326,766,791]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" value="1953-02">February 1953</date>
(Deed C. Thurman).” However, the 
<typeStatus box="[446,543,803,827]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">paratype</typeStatus>
is labeled with the same locality as the 
<typeStatus box="[988,1090,802,827]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
